data.text: @BellaWallerstei I do too,what are you watching bella?
@BellaWallerstei How was it? Doco was superb.
@BellaWallerstei Last night I went to see Get Back: The Rooftop Concert. I was one of only six people there for the screening -- at the biggest cinema in the multiplex, and with the best sound.
@BellaWallerstei A night out at the cinema is pretty pricey these days...
@BellaWallerstei Maybe it's more to do with the Tories handling of Covid rather than the virus?
@BellaWallerstei They’re all at Cineworld. £3 a ticket. They’ve worked out they make loads more on the snacks!
@BellaWallerstei They must be showing a Downing Street briefing co-starring Whitty and Valance?
@BellaWallerstei All depends on the film? Last week we went to Uncharted and it was in the best cinema in Malmö. 60% full
@BellaWallerstei Bet it’s in Norfolk, the top Covid County in Uk
